summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Sections 23.47.002, 23.47.008, 23.47.012 and 23.47.013 of the Seattle Municipal Code and adding a new chapter 23.72 to the Seattle Municipal Code to create the 12th Avenue Overlay District; adopting amendments to the Official Land Use Map, Chapter 23.32 to establish the 12th Avenue Overlay District.
